OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry and bright through
OL,6,FSunday with plenty of sunshine at
OL,7,Ffirst. A veil of high cloud will
OL,8,Fspread across the region during the
OL,9,Fafternoon turning the sunshine hazy.
OL,10,FWarm, particularly along the north
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine and dry end to the
OL,14,Fday, bur showery outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fwill spread in overnight, with a small
OL,16,Fchance of the odd rumble of thunder.
OL,17,FMild for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
