OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FShowery outbreaks of rain will
OL,6,Fmove east across the region during the
OL,7,Fmorning, followed by a dry, brighter a
OL,8,Fwarm afternoon across Devon and
OL,9,FCornwall.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSpells
OL,12,Fof rain possible at times over the
OL,13,Fnext few days, but some drier,
OL,14,Fbrighter and warmers intervals in
OL,15,Fbetween. Breezy at times and
OL,16,Ftemperatures around the seasonal
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
